      • replace

        public StompContentSubframe replace(ByteBuf content)
        Description copied from class: DefaultByteBufHolder
        Returns a new ByteBufHolder which contains the specified content.

        Override this method to return a new instance of this object whose content is set to the specified content. The default implementation of DefaultByteBufHolder.copy(), DefaultByteBufHolder.duplicate() and DefaultByteBufHolder.retainedDuplicate() invokes this method to create a copy.
